description: This file contains backend API implementations for the COSA Data Model Library, specifically related to GatewayInfo configuration parameters. It includes function stubs for retrieving parameter values such as boolean, integer, ulong, and string types, with some string parameters implemented to call external data access functions.

methods.name: BOOL GatewayInfo_GetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL * pBool)
methods.description: Retrieves boolean parameter values for GatewayInfo; current implementation is a stub that always returns FALSE.

methods.name: BOOL GatewayInfo_GetParamIntValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,int * pInt)
methods.description: Retrieves integer parameter values for GatewayInfo; current implementation is a stub that always returns FALSE.

methods.name: BOOL GatewayInfo_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameter values for GatewayInfo; current implementation is a stub that always returns FALSE.

methods.name: ULONG GatewayInfo_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pulSize)
methods.description: Retrieves string parameter values for GatewayInfo like ManufacturerOUI, ProductClass, SerialNumber by calling external data access functions.
